snippet.title: Ambers Silk Nightie. Johnny Depp Stunned At Amber Heard's Raw Meat Claim.
snippet.description:
A tale about raw meat stuns everyone when Amber Heard testifies about Johnny Depp's meat rampage. Doctor Shannon Curry predicted some of the ways in which Amber would embellish a tale, here we see it in full effect. The defamation trial between the two celebrities continues in Fairfax, Virginia.
